You can set the location in the /etc/apache2/httpd.conf file:
<VirtualHost *>
ServerName YourServerName
DocumentRoot /home/YourHomeFolder/www
</Virtualhost>
/var/www is owned by root

/home/YourHomeFolder/www is owned by your user 


